# Project: spiderfeet-widget stack

## Stack

- **Node** + webpack (`webpack.common.js`, `npm start` / `npm run build`)
- **UI:** HTML in `src/html/content.html`, SASS → `src/sass/content.scss`
- **JS:** IIFEs under `src/js/`, namespace `window.Widgets`
- **Vendor bundle:** Bootstrap 5.3, jQuery, D3 (via webpack MergeIntoSingleFilePlugin)
- **Output:** `dist/` — iFrame-embeddable `index.html`, `widget.js`, `widget.css`

## Key paths

| Artifact | Path |
|----------|------|
| Page markup | `src/html/content.html` |
| Widget modules | `src/js/*.js` (concat order = folder order) |
| Icons (from backend) | `src/assets/icons/` (copied from spiderfeet analysis) |
| Force graph colours | `@spiderfeet/.docs/analysis/force_graph_colour_scheme.md` |

## Skills

- `.cursor/skills/bootstrap/SKILL.md` — layout, navbar, tabs, connection widget
- `.cursor/skills/d3js/SKILL.md` — force graph, zoom, tooltips
- `.cursor/skills/cursor-multi-repo/SKILL.md` — cross-root work

## Conventions

- `body { overflow: hidden }` — scroll inside panels, not the iframe body
- Parent ↔ widget messaging via `Widgets.Events` (not ad-hoc postMessage)
- Desktop-first layout (no mobile optimisation in stages 0–4)
- Non-Maps tabs (Enrichments, Composer, Logs, Tests): empty placeholder pages until their stage stories land
- API calls target spiderfeet FastAPI base URL (never TypeDB directly)

## Verification

- `npm run build` before merge
- `npm start` for local dev (default port 4001)
